# Game of Life

###Description
C++ implementation of the [Conway's Game of Life](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conway%27s_Game_of_Life)

Both of the following implementation have been written having in mind the Xeon PHI machine as target.

- In the [thread_version](./thread_version) folder, there is the implementation of GOL using low level threading mechanisms.

- In the [fastflow_version](./fastflow_version) folder, there is the implementation of GOL that use the [FastFlow framework](http://calvados.di.unipi.it/).

